    "deskripsi_bisnis": "PT Supreme Cable Manufacturing & Commerce Tbk, together with its subsidiaries, manufactures and sells cables, insulation, cable-related products and raw materials, and melamine products in Indonesia and internationally. The company offers high voltage power cables; medium voltage cable that include armour and non armour cables, lead sheath cables, and spacer cables; low voltage power cables, such as PVC insulated and AL PVC/XLPE insulated cables; building wires; flexible and instrumental cables; and solar cables. It also provides fire resistant, airport lighting, fiber optic, telecommunication, bare conductor, enamelled, and railway cables. PT Supreme Cable Manufacturing & Commerce Tbk was founded in 1970 and is headquartered in Jakarta, Indonesia.",
